ProtoResult:
. "If $ \lim_{x\to x_0} f(x)=L_1 \lim_{x\to x_0} g(x)= L_2, $ 
   then $$ \lim_{x\to x_0} (f+g)(x)\ar= L_1+L_2,\\ \lim_{x\to 
   x_0} (f-g)(x)\ar= L_1-L_2,\\ \lim_{x\to x_0} (fg)(x)\ar= 
   L_1L_2,\\ and, if $L_2\ne0$,\\ \lim_{x\to x_0} (\frac{f}{g} 
   )(x)\ar= \frac{L_1}{ L_2}. $$"
